$PACKAGE APAP.LAPAP
SUBROUTINE LAPAP.V.FT.LOAN.RESTRICT.RT
*------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
*Modification History
*DATE                       WHO                         REFERENCE                                   DESCRIPTION
